metadata.name: NEW WAVE #1
metadata.description:
new wave is my genesis music nft.

new wave is a coming of age, 80â€™s inspired track which dives into the pressures that are faced when transitioning from innocence into a party filled adulthood. it also brings to light the tug of war that substances and alcohol create from within and how eventually one side must win. in this instance, i end the track with a cry for help begging to be taken back into the lifestyle i thrived in as a child before this spiritual warfare began.

i'm so excited to share my first music nft with you and for it to be a song that has a lot of meaning to me. thank you to all of you that have supported me since day 1. i would not be here without you.
